itemDescription: President of the Royal College of Psychiatrists

wikipedia_page.main: Wendy Katherine Burn  (born 1958) is a Consultant in Old Age Psychiatry. She was President of the Royal College of Psychiatrists from 2017 to 2020.

response: Wessely was succeeded as president by Professor Wendy Burn in June 2017.
